Infographic: BJP win expected to expedite the cleanup of the Ganga 
14-3-2017 
BJP win expected to expedite the cleanup of the Ganga

With the BJP’s victory in Uttar Pradesh and Uttarakhand, expectations are high that PM Modi’s ambitious ‘Namami Gange’ programme will give the Ganga cleaning mission a boost. Here’s a look what is being done, the projects completed and what’s to be implemented. 
